"""
PURPOSE: Store time-varying features that change with each transaction
FORMAT: Parquet with timestamp partitioning
CONTENTS:
- transaction_id: Unique transaction identifier
- timestamp: Transaction time
- rolling_avg_7d: 7-day rolling average transaction amount
- transaction_velocity_1h: Number of transactions in last hour
- time_since_last_tx: Seconds since last transaction
- amount_zscore: Standardized deviation from customer mean
- hour_of_day: Transaction hour (0-23)
- day_of_week: Transaction day (0-6)
- is_weekend: Weekend flag
- seasonality_factor: Time-based risk multiplier
- location_distance: Distance from usual locations
"""